20construct*20the*20area*20required*20by*20at*20the*20same*20time*20reducing*20our*20demand*20and*20by*20starting*20the*20necessary*20infrastructure*20projects*20today*20everywhere*20around*20the*20world.*20Otherwise*20the*20consequences*20are*20unthinkable.*3C*2Fp*3E*0A*3Cp*3E***3Csmall*3EAs*20for*20nuclear*20power*2C*20it*20currently*20produces*20*3Ca*20href*3D*22http*3A*2F*2Fen.wikipedia.org*2Fwiki*2FNuclear_power*22*3E2.5*25*3C*2Fa*3E*20of*20the*20world*26rsquo*3Bs*20energy*20or*2010*20quadrillion*20Btu*20per*20year.*20In*202008*2C*20the*20International*20Atomic*20Energy*20Agency*20(IAEA)*20*3Ca*20href*3D*22http*3A*2F*2Fwww.iaea.org*2FNewsCenter*2FNews*2F2008*2Fnp2008.html*22*3Epredicted*3C*2Fa*3E*20that*20nuclear*20power*20capacity*20could*20double*20by*202030*2C*20though*20that*20would*20not*20be*20enough*20to*20increase*20nuclear*26rsquo*3Bs*20share*20of*20electricity*20generation.*20As*20for*20the*20non-renewable*20resource*20of*20uranium*2C*20according*20to*20the*20nuclear*20industry*26rsquo*3Bs*20own*3Ca*20href*3D*22http*3A*2F*2Fwww.world-nuclear.org*2Finfo*2Finf75.html*22*3Eestimation*3C*2Fa*3E*3A*3C*2Fsmall*3E*3C*2Fp*3E*0A*3Cblockquote*3E*0A*3Cp*3ECurrent*20usage*20is*20about*2065*2C000*20tU*2Fyr.*20Thus*20the*20world*26rsquo*3Bs*20present*20measured*20resources*20of*20uranium*20(5.5*20Mt)*20in*20the*20cost*20category*20somewhat*20below*20present*20spot*20prices*20and*20used*20only*20in*20conventional*20reactors*2C*20are*20enough*20to*20last*20for*20over*2080*20years.*3C*2Fp*3E*0A*3C*2Fblockquote*3E*0A*3Cp*3E80*20years*20does*20not*20equal*20sustainable.*20And*20this*20is*20only*20assuming*20current*20use*20rates*20(the*205*25*20of*20world*20energy*20needs).*3C*2Fp*3E*0A*3Cp*3E*3Csmall*3EAn*20average*20plant*20puts*20out*203*20cubic*20meters*20of*20spent*20fuel*20each*20year.*20Assuming*201000*20plants*20operating*20around*20the*20world*20(there*20are*20500*20today)*2C*20that*20would*20makes*203*2C000*20cubic*20meters*20per*20year.*20Over*20those*2080*20